(113,	81,	'en',	'Fast adapt self-adapting chamber setting',	'O:15:\"Nette\\ArrayHash\":4:{s:4:\"text\";s:571:\"<p><span>Our patended system of doctor blade housing and self-adjusting chamber setting compensates for doctor blade wear by maintaining a constant angle to the anilox sleeve surface throughout blade life. An unchanged doctor blade geometry ensures longer life depending on blade type and eliminates pressure changes. The self-adjusting setting eliminates the influence of pressure changes in the inking system on the doctor blade chamber position and doctor blade. This also allows the doctor blade chamber to return to its operating position after throw-off.</span></p>\";s:7:\"x_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"y_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";}'),
