(141,	88,	'en',	'Sleeve handling system',	'O:15:\"Nette\\ArrayHash\":4:{s:4:\"text\";s:466:\"<p><span>The sleeve handling system is an effective tool for moving heavy items in the print unit area. Either hydraulic platform or individual, electrically driven stands are available. On the hydraulic system the operator has to manually operate the bridge and sleeve set to the required positions. Individual stands have motorised supported shafts enabling the bridge and sleeve sets to be located to the required positions with minimum opertor effort.</span></p>\";s:7:\"x_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"y_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";}'),
