(188,	99,	'ru',	'',	'O:15:\"Nette\\ArrayHash\":4:{s:4:\"text\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"x_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"y_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";}'),
(189,	100,	'en',	'Intuitive control',	'O:15:\"Nette\\ArrayHash\":4:{s:4:\"text\";s:499:\"<p><span>A main touch screen control panel with user friendly interface indicates error displays and setting of job parameters. An auxiliary control panel in the unwind and rewind sections ensures quick and comfortable roll handling. The control panels include graphic menu for job parameter settings and diagnostic. The menu is logically and comfortably arranged to display the correct position in real press time. Dedicated screens are connected with the main menu through colour codes.</span></p>\";s:7:\"x_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"y_coord\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";}'),
