(312,	'page',	'en',	'Tradition',	'Tradition',	'Tradition',	'Tradition',	'Tradition',	'Tradition',	6,	'<p><span>Soma has evolved from a local and traditional manufacturer of special-purpose machines into a</span><br /><span>recognized global player within the flexible printing and packaging industry. This success would</span><br /><span>have not been possible without the vision and commitment of its founder. &ldquo;The goals we have</span><br /><span>achieved, and the tradition from which we were founded is in essence the driving force for new</span><br /><span>challenges.&rdquo;</span></p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-04 13:08:49',	43,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(313,	'page',	'en',	'Quality',	'Quality',	'Quality',	'Quality',	'Quality',	'Quality',	5,	'<p>High quality machines ensure long term success and prosperity. The performance, reliability, comfort<br />and maintenance costs of all Soma printing and packaging products are key areas where quality<br />and engineering play a crucial role. All key mechanical parts for Soma machines are manufactured</p>\r\n<p>in-house,&nbsp;with emphasis on the precise production of parts, accurate&nbsp;assembly and&nbsp;uncompromising</p>\r\n<p>quality control at every stage from design to final assembly and&nbsp;beyond.</p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-04 13:18:04',	44,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
