(421,	'page',	'en',	'Owners Credo',	'Owners Credo',	'Owners Credo',	'Owners Credo',	'Owners Credo',	'Owners Credo',	11,	'<p>I believe that the road to success is based on competence, confidence and passion. COMPETENCE - a deep understanding of the customer&rsquo;s business. CONFIDENCE - in yourself and your team. PASSION - to implement ideas that others consider impossible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Above all, it is &lsquo;face to face&rsquo; relationships that are important for long term success. Fair play and fair business practice is essential.</p>\r\n<p><em>Ladislav Verner</em><br /><em>General Manager</em></p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-05 15:12:59',	28,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(422,	'page',	'cs',	'Krédo majitele',	'Krédo majitele',	'Krédo majitele',	'Krédo majitele',	'Krédo majitele',	'Krédo majitele',	9,	'<p>Domn&iacute;v&aacute;m se, že k &uacute;spěchu vede jen jedin&aacute; cesta. Cesta, kter&aacute; je založena na kompetentnosti, zdrav&eacute; sebedůvěře a hlavně na siln&eacute;m zaujet&iacute;. KOMPETENTNOST ch&aacute;pu jako detailn&iacute; znalost potřeb z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ka, SEBEDŮVĚROU m&aacute;m na mysli v&iacute;ru v sebe sama a svůj t&yacute;m a ZAUJET&Iacute; jako hnac&iacute; s&iacute;lu k prosazen&iacute; pr&aacute;vě těch n&aacute;padů, kter&eacute; ostatn&iacute; považuj&iacute; za nemožn&eacute;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To v&scaron;e dohromady opřeno o osobn&iacute; vztah a důvěru vede k dlouhodob&eacute;mu &uacute;spěchu. Fair Play a Fair Business je to, co j&aacute; považuji za podstatn&eacute;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em>Ladislav Verner</em><br /> <em>majitel</em></p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-05 15:12:59',	28,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
