(426,	'page',	'en',	'Company History',	'Company History',	'Company History',	'Company History',	'Company History',	'Company History',	6,	'<h2>SOMA is a dynamically developing company with a rich history, a solid production range and a unique know-how resulting in long-term success.</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Launched in the early nineties, the Soma range of machines for flexible packaging production include flexographic printing presses, slitter rewinders, laminators, coaters, plate mounters, sheeters and die cutters. All products are manufactured and assembled entirely in-house enabling the company to oversee all aspects of production and quality control.</p>\r\n<p>Continuous growth over the past few years has seen the establishment of a new production and administration complex encompassing both research and development. More recently new innovations in product design have resulted in further growth leading to investment in the Soma Globe centre where customers are able to run product and development trials using the latest machines in the Soma range. The company is committed to developing new products with added value and to providing long-term service and maintenance to ensure the longevity of its products.</p>\r\n<p>Participation at key industry exhibitions has been instrumental in building a strong sales and support network of distribution channels throughout the world leading to 90 percent of product going to export. The company&rsquo;s ethos is based on good business practice and high quality products supported by a work force trained to the highest standards in their respective fields.</p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-05 15:16:32',	30,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(427,	'page',	'cs',	'Historie společnosti',	'Historie společnosti',	'Historie společnosti',	'Historie společnosti',	'Historie společnosti',	'Historie společnosti',	1,	'<h2>Společnost SOMA je dynamicky se rozv&iacute;jej&iacute;c&iacute; firmou s bohatou minulost&iacute;, stabiln&iacute;m v&yacute;robn&iacute;m programem a vlastn&iacute;m know-how, tvoř&iacute;c&iacute;m z&aacute;kladn&iacute; pil&iacute;ře jej&iacute;ho &uacute;spě&scaron;n&eacute;ho a dlouhodob&eacute;ho rozvoje.</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>V&yacute;robn&iacute; program je od poč&aacute;tků devades&aacute;t&yacute;ch let zaměřen na&nbsp; v&yacute;voj a v&yacute;robu vysoce kvalitn&iacute;ch speci&aacute;ln&iacute;ch jedno&uacute;čelov&yacute;ch zař&iacute;zen&iacute;, strojů na zpracov&aacute;n&iacute; a potisk materi&aacute;lu, zejm&eacute;na pak flexotiskov&yacute;ch strojů,&nbsp;<br />pod&eacute;ln&yacute;ch řezaček, mont&aacute;žn&iacute;ch stolic, lamin&aacute;torů, př&iacute;čn&yacute;ch řezaček a vysek&aacute;vac&iacute;ch automatů. Společnost proch&aacute;z&iacute; trvalou expanz&iacute;, byly vybudov&aacute;ny nov&eacute; produkčn&iacute;, administrativn&iacute; a technologick&eacute; budovy.&nbsp;<br />Inovace a modern&iacute; design jsou kl&iacute;čov&yacute;mi faktory &uacute;spěchu firmy. Společnost SOMA se &uacute;častn&iacute; hlavn&iacute;ch veletrhů a vybudovala silnou s&iacute;ť obchodn&iacute;ch z&aacute;stupců ve vět&scaron;ině světov&yacute;ch regionů.&nbsp;<br />Z&aacute;kladn&iacute; předpoklad &uacute;spě&scaron;n&eacute;ho rozvoje firmy spoč&iacute;v&aacute; v dobr&eacute;m obchodn&iacute;m pl&aacute;nu a t&yacute;mov&eacute; spolupr&aacute;ci kvalifikovan&yacute;ch expertů.</p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-05 15:16:32',	30,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(428,	'page',	'en',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	6,	'<p><span>Our target was to build a common meetings place for our experts, suppliers, partners and customers at the highest level. The result is the Soma Globe technology and training centre.</span><br /><br /><span>A combination of R&amp;D facilities with showroom and printing and converting machines, the Soma Globe centre offers unlimited possibilities.</span><br /><br /><span>Soma</span><span>&nbsp;customers will appreciate the new demonstration and training area where they can utilise our printing and converting machines for product testing, operator training, new development trials and where they will gain maximum confidence in the Soma brand and important support for their business.</span></p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-05 15:18:41',	31,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(429,	'page',	'cs',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	'Soma Globe',	1,	'<p><span>Na&scaron;&iacute;m snem bylo vytvořit m&iacute;sto pro společn&aacute; setk&aacute;n&iacute; na&scaron;ich expertů, dodavatelů, partnerů a z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ků na nejvy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute; &uacute;rovni. Podařilo se n&aacute;m vybudovat modern&iacute; technologick&eacute; a &scaron;kolic&iacute; centrum splňuj&iacute;c&iacute; nejpř&iacute;sněj&scaron;&iacute; krit&eacute;ria na odborn&eacute;, vysoce kvalifikovan&eacute; zař&iacute;zen&iacute;.</span><br /><br /><span>D&iacute;ky kombinaci R&amp;D z&aacute;zem&iacute; a showroomu s tiskařsk&yacute;mi a zpracovatelsk&yacute;mi stroji nab&iacute;z&iacute; neomezen&eacute; možnosti pro uspokojen&iacute; potřeb v&scaron;ech, kteř&iacute; do něj se sv&yacute;mi požadavky vstupuj&iacute;.</span><br /><br /><span>Z&aacute;kazn&iacute;ci ocen&iacute; nov&eacute; prezentačn&iacute;, demo a &scaron;kolic&iacute; prostory. Mohou využ&iacute;t kapacity tiskařsk&yacute;ch a zpracovatelsk&yacute;ch strojů pro testov&aacute;n&iacute; vlastn&iacute;ch v&yacute;robků, za&scaron;kolov&aacute;n&iacute; obsluhy i testov&aacute;n&iacute; technologick&yacute;ch novinek. Z&iacute;skaj&iacute; tak maxim&aacute;ln&iacute; důvěru ve značku Soma a poc&iacute;t&iacute; důležitou podporu pro jejich podnik&aacute;n&iacute;.</span></p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-05 15:18:42',	31,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
(430,	'page',	'en',	'Slitter rewinders',	'Slitter rewinders',	'Slitter rewinders',	'Slitter rewinders',	'Slitter rewinders',	'Slitter rewinders',	7,	'<p><span>The SOMA slitter rewinder range is comprised of the PLANET group and is a comprehensive series of modular machines capable of handling a wide range of paper, films, foils and laminates. All are available with the latest technology in slitter rewinder design, depending on customer requirements, including web edge guides, vacuum splicing tables, precise tension control units with AC or pneumatic braking, automatic knife positioning, automatic laser core positioning and intuitive touch screen controls.</span></p>',	'',	'published',	NULL,	NULL,	'2012-12-05 15:21:09',	10,	'',	'',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL),
